Interface BaseDao<T>

All Known Subinterfaces:
GameDao, LeagueDao, MembershipDao, SeasonDao, TeamDao, UserDao
All Known Implementing Classes:
GameDaoImpl, LeagueDaoImpl, MembershipDaoImpl, SeasonDaoImpl, TeamDaoImpl, UserDaoImpl
public interface BaseDao<T>

An interface for database operations. The BaseDao interface provides a method for inserting records to the database. The BaseDao interface provides a method for deleting records from the database.
